3. Run docs checks after docs reconciliation: `npm run check:contract-recheck`, `npm run check:deferred-claims`, `npm run check:frontend-closure`, and `npm run check:docs-maturity-sync`.
4. Finish with `npm run test:readiness` and `npm run quality:check` from a clean working state, preserving unrelated user/generated work.

